1
Physical layer
Converts data to wireless/electrical signals 
2
Data link layer
Ensures reliable & error free data.
3
Network layer
Selects the best path to route data over the network
4
Transport layer
Established reliable connections
5
Session layer
Manage communication sessions
6
Presentation layer
Formats data so that its recognizable by applications
Encryption & decryption
7
Application layer
Provides interface by which users can access the network
